Revision history for Padre-Plugin-XML

0.11    to be released
        removed unnecessary code in document class (ZENOG)
        Padre::Plugin::XML::Document => Padre::Document::XML (ZENOG)
        Padre::Task::SyntaxChecker::XML => Padre::Document::XML::Syntax (ZENOG)
        fix syntax checking (ZENOG)
        Padre 0.81 compatibility (ZENOG)
        Switch to Module::Install (SZABGAB)

0.10    2010.08.25
        fix ticket #943: crash on serialization of Task::SyntaxChecker::XML
        (ZENOG)
        compatibility with newer versions of Padre (ZENOG)
        improved README file (ZENOG)
        gettext-ified some strings (ZENOG)
        Task API 2 compatibility (CHORNY)
        auto syntax check works in new Padre (CHORNY)
        Padre::Document::XML => Padre::Plugin::XML::Document (CHORNY)

0.06    2009.05.31
        removed taint mode for tests, leading to build failures (jquelin)

0.05    2009.2.1
        catch and report some errors (HJANSEN)
        do not try to tidy non-XML documents (HJANSEN)
        enable folding (HJANSEN)
        for Padre 0.26

0.04    2009.1.5
        for Padre 0.23

0.03    2008.12.24
        added syntax checking capabilities (HJANSEN)
        comment_lines_str (FAYLAND)

0.02
        add a new Padre::Document::XML

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

